Author: lolstraightwhiteboys
Text: Because I realized that my ED symptoms were making me miserable. They were exacerbating my self harm problem and impeding my recovery from various other mental health issues. But now my symptoms are making me feel happier (well restricting anyway, not binging and purging), and I don’t see myself ever recovering anyway, so I don’t see the point in stopping.

Author: bobeta
Text: Why did you ask for for help four months ago? Are those reasons still true?
